## 🚧 Running Your Own Evolution

### Quick Start
```bash
# For immediate results with pre-trained state
python quick_start.py --load-evolved-state

# For full evolution from scratch (72+ hours)
python main.py --full-evolution --target="theory_of_everything"

# For custom problem solving
python main.py --problem="your_research_question" --max-cycles=10
```

### Monitoring Evolution
```bash
# Real-time monitoring
python monitor.py --live-view

# View evolution history
python analyze_cycles.py --cycles=1-14 --generate-report
```

