## 🔄 Extending the System

### Creating Custom Hemispheres

```python
# custom_hemisphere.py
from crewai import Agent

class QuantumGravityHemisphere(Agent):
    def __init__(self):
        super().__init__(
            role="Quantum Gravity Specialist",
            goal="Unify quantum mechanics with general relativity",
            backstory="Evolved to bridge quantum and relativistic domains",
            tools=[mathematical_modeling, spacetime_analysis],
            allow_delegation=True
        )
    
    def process_problem(self, problem):
        # Custom quantum gravity reasoning
        return self.unified_field_analysis(problem)
```

### Adding New Problem Domains

```python
# domain_config.py
RESEARCH_DOMAINS = {
    "consciousness": {
        "initial_hemispheres": ["logical", "creative", "philosophical"],
        "target_metrics": ["coherence", "testability", "novelty"],
        "complexity_threshold": 0.85
    },
    "climate_modeling": {
        "initial_hemispheres": ["mathematical", "experimental", "systems"],
        "target_metrics": ["accuracy", "predictive_power", "scalability"],
        "complexity_threshold": 0.90
    }
}
```

